<p><strong>Oysters and Shellfish:</strong> Muscadet-sur-Lie and Sancerre have long accompanied plateaux de fruits de mer. The wine's salinity and mineral content echo the ocean's brine, while its acidity brightens the shellfish's natural sweetness without masking delicate flavors.</p>

